### Test Portal Content API Routes
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar HTTP clients

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Get all portal apps (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/portal-apps
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 2. Get active portal apps (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/public/portal-apps
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 3. Create new portal app
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/portal-apps
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "V2Ray Android",
  "description": "کلاینت V2Ray برای اندروید - نسخه جدید",
  "downloadLink": "https://example.com/v2ray-android.apk",
  "qrCode": "https://example.com/qr-code.png",
  "videoUrl": "https://youtube.com/watch?v=example",
  "iconUrl": "https://example.com/v2ray-icon.png",
  "order": 1,
  "isActive": true
}

###

### 4. Update portal app
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/portal-apps/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "V2Ray Android - بروزرسانی شده",
  "description": "آخرین نسخه با ویژگی‌های جدید"
}

###

### 5. Delete portal app
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/portal-apps/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 6. Get all announcements (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/portal-announcements
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 7. Get active announcements (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/public/portal-announcements
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 8. Create new announcement
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/portal-announcements
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "بروزرسانی مهم سرورها",
  "content": "سرورهای ایران در تاریخ ۱۴۰۳/۰۸/۱۵ برای بروزرسانی از ساعت ۲ تا ۴ صبح قطع خواهند بود.",
  "type": "warning",
  "priority": 10,
  "isActive": true
}

###

### 9. Update announcement
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/portal-announcements/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "type": "success",
  "content": "بروزرسانی با موفقیت انجام شد. تمام سرورها آنلاین هستند."
}

###

### 10. Delete announcement
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/portal-announcements/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### Sample data for testing multiple apps

### Create App 1 - V2Ray Android
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/portal-apps
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "V2Ray Android",
  "description": "بهترین کلاینت برای اندروید",
  "downloadLink": "https://github.com/2dust/v2rayNG/releases/latest",
  "order": 1,
  "isActive": true
}

